[IMG]http://i34.photobucket.com/albums/d108/fgfuyfyuiuyf/xcv.jpg[/img]

[IMG]http://i34.photobucket.com/albums/d108/fgfuyfyuiuyf/woman.png[/img]

[IMG]http://i34.photobucket.com/albums/d108/fgfuyfyuiuyf/no.png[/img]
...and you can't teleport because it says your in wildy...
Help?
